==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tagtail
<hw>Tag"tail`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A worm
which has its tail conspicuously colored.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person who attaches himself to another against the
will of the latter; a hanger-on.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Taguan</ent>⟦br⟧
